<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> <span class="c3">{لاَ يَرْجُونَ حِسَابًا}</span>: <span class="c2">«لاَ يَخَافُونَهُ»</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>